{"title":"Grow Some Horns for Your Bike Helmet with Magnetic Helmet Flair","link":"https://bikerumor.com/bike-helmet-magnetic-helmet-flair-horns-ears/","date":1749222000000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-first-picture-e1748966016724.webp\" width=\"638\" height=\"535\" alt=\"(Photo / Helmet Flair)\" /></p>\n<p>I got an email the other day from Shaun Maple of the brand <a href=\"https://helmetflair.com/collections/bicycle\" target=\"_blank\">Helmet Flair</a>. Shaun is the self-proclaimed “Father of Flair” and someone I was supposed to meet with at Sea Otter this last April. But alas, time got away from me at the event, and I missed the opportunity to meet. I wanted to meet with him because I was interested to learn more about Helmet Flair.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-hero.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1169\" height=\"1169\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-hero.webp\" alt=\"Helmet Flair hero\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-hero.webp 1169w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-hero-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-hero-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-hero-768x768.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photo / Helmet Flair)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Shaun’s goal/mission at Helmet Flair is simple: “<em>increase helmet use by making the helmets awesome</em>“. To do that, the brand has  two product lines that appeal to cyclists, skaters, and motorcycle riders: <a href=\"https://helmetflair.com/collections/large-horns\" target=\"_blank\">MagNeatOhz</a> and <a href=\"https://helmetflair.com/collections/softeez\" target=\"_blank\">Softeez</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-nubbins.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"631\" height=\"407\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-nubbins.webp\" alt=\"Helmet Flair nubbins\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-nubbins.webp 631w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-nubbins-297x192.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-nubbins-120x77.webp 120w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-applying-nubbins.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-applying-nubbins.webp\" alt=\"Helmet Flair applying nubbins\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-applying-nubbins.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-applying-nubbins-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-applying-nubbins-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-applying-nubbins-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-applying-nubbins-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-applying-nubbins-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-nubbins-aplication.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-nubbins-aplication.webp\" alt=\"Helmet Flair nubbins aplication\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-nubbins-aplication.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-nubbins-aplication-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-nubbins-aplication-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-nubbins-aplication-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-nubbins-aplication-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-nubbins-aplication-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>MagNeatOhz attach to the helmet using a patented magnetic base called Nubbins. This allows users to swap out their flair easily, as well as letting the flair pop off in the case of an impact. The Softeez have a soft foam design that is applied with a peel-and-stick attachment.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-softeez-black.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"946\" height=\"541\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-softeez-black.webp\" alt=\"Helmet Flair softeez black\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-softeez-black.webp 946w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-softeez-black-297x170.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-softeez-black-120x69.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-softeez-black-768x439.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-banana.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-banana.webp\" alt=\"Helmet Flair banana\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-banana.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-banana-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-banana-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-banana-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-banana-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-banana-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Some of the fun designs that you can choose from include cat ears, horns, unicorn horns, and even a banana through the head. All of the products are made in the USA. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-packaging.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1187\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-packaging.webp\" alt=\"Helmet Flair packaging\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-packaging.webp 1187w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-packaging-278x300.webp 278w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-packaging-111x120.webp 111w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-packaging-768x828.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-in-use.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"460\" height=\"438\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-in-use.webp\" alt=\"Helmet Flair in use\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-in-use.webp 460w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-in-use-297x283.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-in-use-120x114.webp 120w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Concern is warranted about putting a protruding piece of hard ABS plastic on your helmet (the same goes for cameras and lights). It may be compromising the helmet’s primary design and function. Even if the Flair is designed to pop off the magnetic base upon impact. Personally, for cyclists, I feel the Softeez may be the better choice.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Just something to think about. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-specs.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"714\" height=\"611\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-specs.webp\" alt=\"Helmet Flair specs\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-specs.webp 714w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-specs-297x254.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Helmet-Flair-specs-120x103.webp 120w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>MagNeatOhz Retail &amp; Detail</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $34.95</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Made in the USA</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Interchangeable tops</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Withstands highway speeds</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Rare-earth magnetic base is strong</li>\n\n\n\n<li>HQ is in Kansas</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Softeez Retail &amp; Detail</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $19.95 ($14.95 for Unicorn Horn)</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Made in the USA</li>\n\n\n\n<li>IEasy peel-and-stick install on any helmet</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Soft material ensures the helmet can do its job</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Great for snow helmets, bike helmets, motorcycle helmets, and skate helmets</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Hit the link below to get your flair on. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://helmetflair.com/\" target=\"_blank\">HelmetFlair.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/bike-helmet-magnetic-helmet-flair-horns-ears/\">Grow Some Horns for Your Bike Helmet with Magnetic Helmet Flair</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"177696d34f694711f8aff5e8e889934ce13bfa3bffb3fe338a0c11007f91fc55","category":"Cycling"}